The Alex Jones Show 
Sunday, 13 December 2009

audio files are divided on half-hour breaks
[sebaygo1]




The 2 hour Sunday show is typically a review of the past week's news and a look forward to the coming week's events.



This broadcast's first hour is a not-very-well-edited-to-fit version of Alex's interview on Tuesday, December 8th of Lord Christopher Monckton, reporting from the Copenhagen summit. 



The second hour includes some of Congressman Ron Paul's appearance on Friday's [Dec. 11th] show, plus other material.
